*Nastavili* smo da se igramo nakon ručka. (We continued to play after lunch.)

*Nastavak* je još uvek u toku. (The continuation is still ongoing.)

Učenici su *nastavili* da uče osnove matematike. (The students continued to learn the basics of mathematics.)

Oni su se *nastavili* kretati napred. (They continued to move forward.)

Svi smo se *nastavili* podsećati naših uspomena. (We all continued to reminisce about our memories.)